title: The All Voicemail Podcast: Part Deux
description: The crew does another all voicemail podcast, taking questions from an angry listener, a guy who got hit by a car, child rearing, read receipts, starfish, keeping secrets, who's the nicest, 4v4v4 battle royale, the best cover songs, two farmers who are both driving tractors, granny syndrome and how to look cool to middle schoolers.
